{"chapter": {"chapterId": "S1", "title": "一、市场竞争态势摘要", "anchor": "section-1-0", "order": 10, "summary": "本章提炼报告核心结论、关键数据与核心策略建议，为全文提供执行摘要。", "blocks": [{"type": "heading", "level": 1, "text": "一、市场竞争态势摘要", "anchor": "section-1-0"}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "本报告摘要呈现北美车载无感互联配件市场的核心洞察。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "level": 2, "text": "1.1 核心结论", "anchor": "section-1-0-1"}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "市场处于认知静默与关联议题沸腾并存的奇特状态。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "level": 2, "text": "1.2 关键数据对比", "anchor": "section-1-0-2"}, {"type": "kpiGrid", "items": [{"label": "北美市场规模（2024）", "value": "5.43亿美元", "unit": "", "delta": "占全球37%", "deltaTone": "up"}, {"label": "预计CAGR（至2033）", "value": "12.7%", "unit": "", "delta": "稳健增长", "deltaTone": "up"}, {"label": "用户核心痛点占比", "value": "28.6%", "unit": "", "delta": "蓝牙连接问题", "deltaTone": "down"}, {"label": "中国供应链毛利率", "value": "35%-50%", "unit": "", "delta": "利润空间可观", "deltaTone": "up"}]}, {"type": "heading", "level": 2, "text": "1.3 核心策略建议", "anchor": "section-1-0-3"}, {"type": "list", "listType": "ordered", "items": [[{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "优先攻克连接稳定性技术瓶颈。"}]}], [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "构建透明可信的数据隐私叙事。"}]}], [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "利用供应链优势聚焦差异化创新。"}]}]]}]}}